Package org.ipdr.api.configuration

Contains API classes for custom configuration implementation.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CollectorConfigI This interface provides configuration of the collector.
ConnectionConfigI This interface provides configuration of a Connection
ExporterConfigI This interface provides configuration of an Exporter
FieldConfigI This interface provides configuration of a field in a template
SessionConfigI This interface provides configuration of a Session
 

Class Summary
CollectorConfigBase The class provides a convenient base for CollectorConfigI implementations
ConnectionConfigBase The class provides a convenient base for ConnectionConfigI implementations
ExporterConfigBase The class provides a convenient base for ExporterConfigI implementations
FieldConfig This class provides a basic implementation of FieldConfigI
SessionConfigBase The class provides a convenient base for SessionConfigI implementations
TemplateConfig Represents a template in the system
 

Exception Summary
ConfigException Exception thrown when there's an error in the configuration data.
 

Package org.ipdr.api.configuration Description

Contains API classes for custom configuration implementation.
